              8.16199618157183e+00  -1.48677252037245e+00   1.07132870205281e+00
              8.20411753797588e+00   1.65172311939115e+00   7.58922443551583e-01
              1.94275936984854e+00   4.16809497690798e-02   2.82615034692660e-02


xcart_lastimg
              0.00000000000000e+00   0.00000000000000e+00   0.00000000000000e+00
